{"title":"Github进行fork后如何与原仓库同步","uid":"1bb5f1b25d5c493ad6a7afdd534feac9","slug":"Github进行fork","date":"2023-08-11T02:13:07.000Z","updated":"2023-08-16T01:07:37.275Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Github进行fork.json","keywords":"生活,美食,java,vue,Web开发,Linux","cover":"/img/photo-4.jpg","content":"<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>首先你找到了你一个你认为优秀的项目</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>写这片博客的原因：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>在GitHub上我们会去fork别人的一个项目，这就在自己的Github上生成了一个与原作者项目互不影响的副本，自己可以将自己Github上的这个项目再clone到本地进行修改，修改后再push，只有自己Github上的项目会发生改变，而原作者项目并不会受影响，避免了原作者项目被污染。但经过一段时间， 有可能作者原来的代码变化很大， 你想接着在他最新的代码上修改， 这时你需要合并原作者的最新代码过来， 让你的项目变成最新的。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>看例子</strong></p>\n<p>第一步：将别人的项目Fork到我们自己的github下，后面无脑创建（不是重点！）</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230815160804529.png\" alt=\"image-20230815160804529 &quot;示例图&quot;\"></p>\n<p>第二步：进入自己的github中找到Fork过来的项目 克隆到本地</p>\n<p><code>git clone  xxx </code></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230815161658564.png\" alt=\"image-20230815161658564\"></p>\n<p>将项目clone到本地（自己找好文件夹  又是无脑操作！！！）</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230815161847527.png\" alt=\"image-20230815161847527\"></p>\n<p>第三步：<font color='red'>进入克隆下来的目录中</font>，然后添加原作者项目的 地址， 然后将代码 fetch 过来</p>\n<p><code>cd xxx</code>  进入项目目录</p>\n<p><code>git remote -v</code></p>\n<p><code>git remote  add upstream xxxx</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230815162518362.png\" alt=\"image-20230815162518362\"></p>\n<p>然后拉取最新的数据(upstream就是个别名 拉取)</p>\n<p><code>git fetch upstream</code></p>\n<p>拉去最新的代码后进行合并到主分支上 （我本来就是最新的 所有无更新）</p>\n<p><code>git breanch</code></p>\n<p><code>git merge upstream/master</code></p>\n<p>如果有冲突的话，需要丢掉本地分支：<br><code>git reset –hard upstream/master</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230815163235483.png\" alt=\"image-20230815163235483\"></p>\n<p>最后：这时你的当前本地的项目变成和原作者的主项目一样了，可以把它提交到你的GitHub库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git commit -am ‘更新到原作者的主分支’</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\">#</span><span class=\"language-bash\">下面的出现冲突后 使用git push -u origin master -f  <span class=\"comment\">#强制提交</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">git push origin </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230815163705003.png\" alt=\"image-20230815163705003\"></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p>注意当你碰到你复制的url地址不能用，删除之前错误的那个<code>git remote 别名</code>，试试ssh地址 这时你再进行<code>git remote xxx </code></p>\n<p>参考如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20230815164034964.png\" alt=\"image-20230815164034964\"></p>\n\n</div>\n","text":"Github进行fork后如何与原仓库同步...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":900,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"github","slug":"github","count":1,"path":"api/categories/github.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"github","slug":"github","count":1,"path":"api/tags/github.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"白兔","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/photo.png","link":"/","description":"一只刚刚入门的小白兔","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/